m_q.target_metric: Most common FIGO_stage value among patients aged above 70
sub_questions: What are the FIGO_stage values for patients above 70?
What is the frequency distribution of FIGO_stage among filtered patients?
Which FIGO_stage has the highest count?

format_notes: Some FIGO_stage values may be missing or null

constraints: FIGO_stage must not be null or empty for counting
Age must be a valid numeric value
derived_filters: Exclude rows where Age is null
Exclude rows where FIGO_stage is null or empty
statistical_tests: Count frequency of each FIGO_stage value
Identify mode (most frequent value) of FIGO_stage
output_format_requirements: Return the single most common FIGO_stage value
Handle ties by reporting all tied values or selecting one consistently
Report count or frequency alongside the result for context
